query:
SELECT DATE(auditDate) as audit_date, COUNT(*) as count 
FROM auditInstances 
WHERE auditDate >= '2025-10-01' AND auditDate <= '2025-12-31'
GROUP BY DATE(auditDate)
ORDER BY audit_date;
